I"“<p>My research interests include</p>

<ul>
  <li><em>Ultrasonics and Wave propagation phenomena,</em></li>
  <li><em>Optical systems and computer vision</em></li>
  <li><em>Sensor Network and Optimization,</em></li>
  <li><em>Structural Health Monitoring and Non-destructive testing,</em></li>
  <li><em>Ray tracing-based modelling and Graph theory,</em></li>
  <li><em>Finite Element Simulations,</em></li>
  <li><em>Hardware-in-loop and real-time systems,</em></li>
  <li><em>Internet of Things</em></li>
</ul>

